Class MeterDifferentImageSubtract

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.DataSourceScalar

    MeterDifferentImageSubtractDoubleSize

    public class MeterDifferentImageSubtract
extends DataSourceScalar
    Uses a Widom-like insertion of a mode to calculate a probability. Uses a different box than the main simulation, to assume a mode & rod are removed
